The paper focuses on the development of a MATLAB-based toolbox for processing large acoustic datasets in the field of bioacoustics. This involves the integration of high-performance computing technologies and data-mining capabilities. Based on this, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). Other likely sub-categories include cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), cs.DB (Databases), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
